{"tid":14703,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"美帝簽證問題","createTime":"2016-11-30T15:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T22:52:29.000Z","uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07525ad1fdfcdfa371298a3bd273811fa6aa00a0","tid":14703,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:18:08.000Z","msg":"本貓搞緊簽證中..<br />\n約左下月初面談...有D緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩要準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d82a4d4c80c89ec65b2b5aaca540a4eaf1d8b7f","tid":14703,"uid":3249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:25:29.000Z","msg":"帶相，帶齊文件<br />\n入到去到你果陣會叫你埋去櫃位問你啲普通問題<br />\n例如你讀緊書定做緊嘢，去果邊做咩<br />\n我就係英文唔叻，佢搵咗人幫我翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前後傾咗十分鐘左右都算輕鬆<br />\n之後會收咗你本passport打埋手指模走得<br />\n<br />\n利申前年簽咗十年"},{"pid":"7002f079bd0dc7af20ee9dabab68531feac376af","tid":14703,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶相，帶齊文件<br />\n入到去到你果陣會叫你埋去櫃位問你啲普通問題<br />\n例如你讀緊書定做緊嘢，去果邊做咩<br />\n我就係英文唔叻，佢搵咗人幫我翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前後傾咗十分鐘左右都算輕鬆<br />\n之後會收咗你本passport打埋手指模走得<br />\n<br />\n利申前年簽咗十年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係我係聽唔到野喎，筆談應該冇問題嗎<br />\n<br />\n但係我要早上去喎...30分鐘前到US consulate?"},{"pid":"7f3866fa106f8f2a1441237897b20a9c580a5b66","tid":14703,"uid":3249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>帶相，帶齊文件<br />\n入到去到你果陣會叫你埋去櫃位問你啲普通問題<br />\n例如你讀緊書定做緊嘢，去果邊做咩<br />\n我就係英文唔叻，佢搵咗人幫我翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前後傾咗十分鐘左右都算輕鬆<br />\n之後會收咗你本passport打埋手指模走得<br />\n<br />\n利申前年簽咗十年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係我係聽唔到野喎，筆談應該冇問題嗎<br />\n<br />\n但係我要早上去喎...30分鐘前到US consulate?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n30分鐘. yes<br />\n記得入去果陣倒哂或者飲哂啲水 會check袋<br />\n<br />\n至於可唔可以用筆就答你唔到"},{"pid":"024d721f348d5f179ba3d4472f970fa0c970438d","tid":14703,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>帶相，帶齊文件<br />\n入到去到你果陣會叫你埋去櫃位問你啲普通問題<br />\n例如你讀緊書定做緊嘢，去果邊做咩<br />\n我就係英文唔叻，佢搵咗人幫我翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前後傾咗十分鐘左右都算輕鬆<br />\n之後會收咗你本passport打埋手指模走得<br />\n<br />\n利申前年簽咗十年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係我係聽唔到野喎，筆談應該冇問題嗎<br />\n<br />\n但係我要早上去喎...30分鐘前到US consulate?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n30分鐘. yes<br />\n記得入去果陣倒哂或者飲哂啲水 會check袋<br />\n<br />\n至於可唔可以用筆就答你唔到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望pass埋架"},{"pid":"15768d4dea9ea3338b752901e6f065ff0be5b34b","tid":14703,"uid":10317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"簽證唔洗擔心 問下你近況同去美國做咩 通常都批<br />\n要擔心不如擔心下入境<br />\n不論係去學術交流定旅遊，入境海關都好麻煩 <br />\n如非必要都唔會去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36571ba3310e25c0437b0de5b83efc890655b56a","tid":14703,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簽證唔洗擔心 問下你近況同去美國做咩 通常都批<br />\n要擔心不如擔心下入境<br />\n不論係去學術交流定旅遊，入境海關都好麻煩 <br />\n如非必要都唔會去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又係喎，我都唔想問到口啞啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa20bbdac5967b76a1e2b91a076be10509cfbfb6","tid":14703,"uid":3249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:26:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簽證唔洗擔心 問下你近況同去美國做咩 通常都批<br />\n要擔心不如擔心下入境<br />\n不論係去學術交流定旅遊，入境海關都好麻煩 <br />\n如非必要都唔會去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能果陣我好彩，過關都只係問咗2句，搞咗3分鐘左右<br />\n不過可能依家又嚴啲<br />\n唔會飛到過去先黎唔比你入掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66664d2a4f03b8ccf7525e4637f10fd7978a2527","tid":14703,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:47:58.000Z","msg":"今日面談，有D緊張姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21013bc395f36abcc58c71393616a39150ed6e8b","tid":14703,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:46:22.000Z","msg":"今日灰爆<br />\n<br />\nDQ左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7fa0782eba174adc1560aa94b511b632067255","tid":14703,"uid":10317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:49:25.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf163612d1e9b71d24a0056061ccea03d2f56d9","tid":14703,"uid":10317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果佢有收你passport 就通常都得。好似係"},{"pid":"064872d8e25ec4ac59f28ccdb1ce72c1452a8232","tid":14703,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔想講，只係答問題上有出入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後唔想用特衰申請美簽算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76efae15386e136f29ae779307342eaa283e77b9","tid":14703,"uid":3936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔想講，只係答問題上有出入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後唔想用特衰申請美簽算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有排都唔洗申請"},{"pid":"8f35